Description:
The web as we know it has to adapt to AI, but what does that look like? In this clip from The GitHub Podcast, host Jason Lengstorf explains why the future isn't just chatbots, but a new, integrated user experience. He predicts a "next jQuery" for AI agents and a new boom in web innovation.
